---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Founder-Built Web Systems for Operational Clarity"
    description="DRN.today builds internal web systems that replace spreadsheets, reduce operational friction, and bring clarity â€” designed and executed by a single accountable founder."
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);">
        <div class="section-narrow text-center">
            <h1 class="hero-gradient mb-24">From Operational Chaos to Clarity</h1>
            <p class="text-large mb-48">
                Founder-built internal systems that replace spreadsheets, reduce friction, and bring control to your business operations.
            </p>
            <div class="flex-center gap-16 flex-wrap">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Describe Your System Challenge</a>
                <a href="#how-i-work" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule a Clarity Call</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Recognition -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-wide">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-48">When Spreadsheets Stop Working</h2>
            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Manual Data Reconciliation</h3>
                    <p>Hours spent daily merging data from multiple spreadsheets and tools that don't communicate.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Lack of Real-time Visibility</h3>
                    <p>Decisions made with outdated information because there's no single source of truth.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Founder Dependency</h3>
                    <p>You're the bottleneck because only you know how all the pieces fit together.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How I Work -->
    <section id="how-i-work" class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-secondary) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);">
        <div class="section-wide">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-48">How I Work: Execution Without Hand-Offs</h2>
            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">01</div>
                    <h3>Single-Point Ownership</h3>
                    <p>From first line of code to deployment and long-term maintenance. No hand-offs, no excuses.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">02</div>
                    <h3>Systems for Daily Use</h3>
                    <p>Built for reliability in daily operations, not as demos or prototypes that fail under real load.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">03</div>
                    <h3>Stability Before Scale</h3>
                    <p>A working system for 100 users is better than a broken one for 1000. Reliability first.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">04</div>
                    <h3>No Scope Creep</h3>
                    <p>Controlled, intentional evolution. We build what's needed, not everything that's possible.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">05</div>
                    <h3>Decisions Documented</h3>
                    <p>Trade-offs explained, architecture reasoned. You understand why we built it this way.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">06</div>
                    <h3>Long-Term Responsibility</h3>
                    <p>What I build, I maintain. Your system evolves with your business, doesn't get abandoned.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-narrow text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-24">Ready to Systematize Your Operations?</h2>
            <p class="text-large mb-48">
                Stop patching broken processes. Start building systems that work.
            </p>
            <div class="flex-center gap-16 flex-wrap">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Describe Your System Challenge</a>
                <a href="#how-i-work" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule a 20-Minute Call</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
